    "Details": "The center torso carries a Heavy PPC and this is supplemented by a Gauss rifle with two tons of ammunition in the left torso. To protect against capacitor explosions, CASE II is mounted in the left torso as well. Each side torso carries a Medium X-Pulse Laser.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Battle Fists</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.06</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Omni</color>\n\n",
